msgid "A2 (dual node, tp=8 + dp=2)"
msgstr "A2（双节点，tp=8 + dp=2）"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/MiniMax-M2.5.md:196
msgid ""
"Since cross-node tensor parallelism (TP) can be unstable, the dual-node "
"guide uses a **tp=8 + dp=2** setup (8 NPUs per node, 16 NPUs total)."
msgstr "由于跨节点张量并行（TP）可能不稳定，双节点指南使用 **tp=8 + dp=2** 的设置（每节点 8 个 NPU，共 16 个 NPU）。"

